OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779789943
OL,3,CMan sought after woman reports
OL,4,Cantisemitic abuse on number 46 bus
OL,6,FSussex Police have released a CCTV
OL,7,Fimage of a man in connection with an
OL,8,Falleged antisemitic hate crime on a
OL,9,Fbus on Sussex.
OL,11,FA woman reported being abused by a
OL,12,Ffellow passenger on the number 46 bus
OL,13,Ftravelling towards Portland Road in
OL,14,FHove at around 2.30pm on April 25.
OL,16,FThe incident is being treated as a
OL,17,Fracially aggravated offence and a hate
OL,18,Fcrime, police have said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
