PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779789943
OL,3,CMan sought after woman reports
OL,4,Cantisemitic abuse on number 46 bus
OL,6,FSussex Police said they are conducting
OL,7,F"focused patrols" in Jewish
OL,8,Fcommunities at synagogues, schools,
OL,9,Fand events.
OL,11,FA month on, officers have released a
OL,12,FCCTV image of a man they want to speak
OL,13,Fto in connection with the
OL,14,Finvestigation.
OL,16,FHe is described as a bald, stocky
OL,17,Fwhite man with a grey beard, 5ft 8in,
OL,18,Fwearing a black jacket, trousers and
OL,19,Ftrainers and a dark-coloured shirt,
OL,20,Fand wearing dark glasses.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
