PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779789943
OL,3,CMan sought after woman reports
OL,4,Cantisemitic abuse on number 46 bus
OL,6,FChief Inspector Dan Eagle said: "This
OL,7,Fwas a distressing incident for the
OL,8,Fvictim and we have been working
OL,9,Falongside Brighton & Hove Buses to
OL,10,Fsecure CCTV footage and evidence.
OL,12,F"We are aware of the significant
OL,13,Fimpact of antisemitic incidents on our
OL,14,FJewish communities here in Sussex. We
OL,15,Fare proactively engaging with
OL,16,Fcommunity leaders to offer support and
OL,17,Freassurance."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779789943
OL,3,CMan sought after woman reports
OL,4,Cantisemitic abuse on number 46 bus
OL,6,F"We will continue to work with our
OL,7,Fcommunities and partners to identify
OL,8,Fany emerging issues and respond to
OL,9,Fthem swiftly to make sure people feel
OL,10,Fsafe and are protected.
OL,12,F"Sussex Police is committed to being
OL,13,Fan anti-racist police service and will
OL,14,Fnot tolerate hate crime against any
OL,15,Fcommunity."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
